UNIX BUILD
==========

Requirements
------------

You'll need the Qt4 development headers.

Copy Ttk headers
----------------

tile-qt needs the 'ttkTheme.h' and 'ttkDecls.h' headers. These are not copied during
install of Tk. Look for the files in the Tk sources and copy them to the
directory containing the other Tk/ttk include files.

Configure
---------

Default configure

$ ./configure

or specify one or more of the configure options:

$ ./configure --prefix=... --with-tcl=... --with-tk=... --with-qt-inc=... --with-qt-lib=...

Default value for qt-inc: /usr/include/qt4
Default value for qt-lib: /usr/lib

Build
-----

$ make

Install
-------

$ make install
